*******************************
APPIUM
*******************************
Open source mobile automation tool
First cross platform tool available(Kalabash for ios only)
Works for native(exclusively for ios and Android),
hybrid(clicking on link will take you to browser)and mobile web apps 
Come from Selenium family i.e Support webdriver API

*******************************
Supported platforms
*******************************
iOS
Android
Firefox OS

*******************************
Language Support
*******************************
Java,C#,Python,Ruby,Javascript

*******************************
Appium Internal Architecture-json  wire protocol
*******************************
json wire protocol[whatever language write automation scripts will reach to Appium server as a 
session object which is language independent
Now this Appium server triggers the methods in mobile

Appium has inbuild framework for iOS and Android